===========
üí´ Beckett
===========

**Hypermedia API Client Framework**

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/beckett.svg
        :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/beckett

.. image:: https://circleci.com/gh/phalt/beckett/tree/master.svg?style=svg
